Name: Snow Mountain
About the game: Try to record the high score as much as possible There are two lines that move in the random direction Hold on to avoid getting out of two lines HP will be reduced if you get out of two lines Be careful, when HP reaches 0, the score is initialized. You can control with the keyboard Accel : Up Arrow Key Move : Left Arrow Key, Right Arrow Key
